- [x] User-friendly error messages

### Default Mode ⏳ [IN PROGRESS]

**File**: `flat/cmd/cli/main.go`

- [x] Check for existing .fmdx in cwd
- [ ] Auto-flatten if no .fmdx exists
- [ ] Error if .fmdx exists
